{"id":388405,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2009/04/【真理部】朝鲜，都江堰和四川石化项目/","date":"2009-04-18T04:56:28Z","modified":"2015-04-07T05:00:44Z","title":"【真理部】朝鲜，都江堰和四川石化项目","content":"<p><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-388406\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/FLeZZLpe_DUWbwm2_x8vQ51gcMdOFNW2Cs5bBM-oGfhSAwAAiQIAAEpQ.jpg\" alt=\"FLeZZLpe_DUWbwm2_x8vQ51gcMdOFNW2Cs5bBM-oGfhSAwAAiQIAAEpQ\" width=\"599\" height=\"457\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/FLeZZLpe_DUWbwm2_x8vQ51gcMdOFNW2Cs5bBM-oGfhSAwAAiQIAAEpQ.jpg 850w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/04/FLeZZLpe_DUWbwm2_x8vQ51gcMdOFNW2Cs5bBM-oGfhSAwAAiQIAAEpQ-300x229.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" /></p>\n<p>1, 有关朝鲜问题的报道一律采用新华社通稿。</p>\n<p>2，都江堰100多孕妇胚胎早死，疑因板房甲醛超标，不采访，不报道，不转载。</p>\n<p>3，对四川石化项目签字仪式和开工典礼不做报道。</p>\n<p>【“真理部”是网民对中国共产党中央委员会宣传部和其下属的各省宣传部，以及国务院新闻办公室，互联网信息办公室，中央文明办，国家新闻出版广电总局，文化部等一系列言论出版审查机构的总称。】</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/zhenlibu.jpg\"><img class=\"align center size-full wp-image-149165\" title=\"zhenlibu\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/zhenlibu.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/zhenlibu.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/05/zhenlibu-300x65.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n","author":35,"categories":[20532,8649],"tags":[28510]}